    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/cd45e077711f5cf31f8f90bfd1aed0cf.poster.avif?t=1771432699\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/cd45e077711f5cf31f8f90bfd1aed0cf.webm?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/cd45e077711f5cf31f8f90bfd1aed0cf.mp4?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><u>180+只真实昆虫！</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由一支微小的两人开发团队打造，Bug &amp; Seek是一款轻松开放、以捕虫和收集生物为主题的模拟/生物收集游戏，带有神秘元素。在Bug &amp; Seek中，你刚刚将一生的积蓄投入购买了一家废弃的昆虫博物馆（虫类博物馆）！曾经是该镇和经济的命脉，但在深夜，有人窃走了所有昆虫。现在，你需要捕捉和出售虫子，完成本地商店的请求，并将昆虫馆重新建设成为该镇的标志性建筑。<strong>成为一名卓越的虫类猎手</strong> 随着你提升捕虫技能、升级装备并扩建昆虫馆，结识当地居民并完成任务，赚取特殊物品，揭示“大虫类劫案”期间真正发生的事情。而且，放松吧！没有错误的选择，无需担心能量水平，足够的时间来完成任务和工作. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*我们正在将 Bug &amp; Seek 本地化为中文。*</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/174f611176133d55b998e5c54fbc1d6e.avif?t=1771432699\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>捕捉虫子</strong> -- 拥有超过175种不同的真实昆虫，包括常见昆虫和一些世界上最稀有和有价值的昆虫，可能性无穷。而且每只虫子都附带一个幽默的标语和真实、有信息价值的简短描述。你再也不会以同样的方式看待真实的昆虫了.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/badcf04514dddec1f8f6dd55fb2ae0dc.poster.avif?t=1771432699\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/badcf04514dddec1f8f6dd55fb2ae0dc.webm?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/badcf04514dddec1f8f6dd55fb2ae0dc.mp4?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定制并扩展你的昆虫馆</strong> -- 从使用的鱼缸到地板、装饰和墙纸，你都可以进行定制。升级你的捕虫设备和衣橱。为昆虫馆建造新的翅膀，打造该镇有史以来最好的昆虫馆。当然，记得填满它的是各种各样的昆虫！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/0e8b623c687268fe18cefb82596acfa5.poster.avif?t=1771432699\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/0e8b623c687268fe18cefb82596acfa5.webm?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/0e8b623c687268fe18cefb82596acfa5.mp4?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索这个世界</strong> -- 昆虫生活在各种各样的栖息地：从草地、沙漠和森林到湿地、海滩和城市环境。而你知道吗？Buggburg拥有所有这些！在每个季节里，探索各种生态环境，而Buggburg繁华的城镇广场位于其中心.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/6926970410cc124492de7fb41399c95d.poster.avif?t=1771432699\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/6926970410cc124492de7fb41399c95d.webm?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/6926970410cc124492de7fb41399c95d.mp4?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与当地居民交流</strong> -- 从市长到草药农夫，结识该镇的19位以上居民，并为他们执行任务，赚取特殊装备和物品、秘密和八卦，甚至可能是俳句.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/e06e61a86c3bdcdb6dfc010c3f17040c.poster.avif?t=1771432699\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/e06e61a86c3bdcdb6dfc010c3f17040c.webm?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/e06e61a86c3bdcdb6dfc010c3f17040c.mp4?t=1771432699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解开谜团</strong> -- 一年前，有人在深夜闯入昆虫馆，窃走了所有的昆虫，这一事件被称为“大虫类劫案”。昆虫馆被关闭，Buggburg经济的一个重要组成部分陷入停滞。作为昆虫馆的新业主，看看你是否能够拼凑出真正发生的事情，解开谜团并揭露罪魁祸首！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/e9f1116a5f9c0add7ca162116068e292.avif?t=1771432699\" width=616 height=348 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265310/extras/4390ae49ede343b9d1130300b1a6b7e1.avif?t=1771432699\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>*注意：不支持具有集成 GPU 的机器，并且可能无法正常运行 Bug &amp; Seek。<br><br><br>不要忘记将游戏加入心愿单并关注，同时加入 Bug &amp; Seek Discord 以保持最新动态！</p></li></ul>",
